{"type":"message","id":"b08eef79","parentId":"0a803502","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:30:34.483Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3AE11AF9D0B64758831D\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"205157820289127@lid\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"120363424964463765@g.us\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Smart project\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"205157820289127@lid\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nY eso que avise era p meterle duro"}],"timestamp":1774798234481}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e1b5b11","parentId":"b08eef79","timestamp":"2026-03-29T15:30:38.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sí. Era para activarte a meterle duro, no para dejarlo en “después”.\n\nSi hoy estás bien de energía:\n- haz la sesión completa\n- sin negociar el arranque\n- primera serie seria rápido y entras en ritmo\n\nSi estás medio fundido:\n- igual entrenas\n- baja un poco volumen o carga\n- pero sostén el hábito\n\nSi quieres, te dejo de una vez el enfoque de hoy en 3 líneas.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9459d9ff081919066324c7e5cbd0c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":6276,"output":103,"cacheRead":5632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12011,"cost":{"input":0.015690000000000003,"output":0.001545,"cacheRead":0.001408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018643000000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774798234483,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9459cd5f4819192f9861342fb4db5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc749d85","parentId":"6e1b5b11","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:37:06.621Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A2F9373003C6DF0568B\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"205157820289127@lid\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"120363424964463765@g.us\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Smart project\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"205157820289127@lid\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nSi tocaria hoy sin embargo no ceeo que entrenemos"}],"timestamp":1774809426618}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b805244","parentId":"bc749d85","timestamp":"2026-03-29T18:37:13.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Entonces claro: **tocaría, pero no parece día para forzarlo**.\n\nSi no van a entrenar hoy, no lo disfraces:\n- hoy queda como **día perdido / no ejecutado**\n- mañana se retoma con intención clara\n- no intentes “compensar” haciendo locuras después\n\nLo útil ahora es decidir bien:\n- si de verdad están muy cruzados, **descanso y ya**\n- si sí hay una ventana mínima, hagan aunque sea una **versión recortada de 30-40 min**\n\nLa clave no es culpa. Es **definir**.\n¿Lo cerramos como descanso real o todavía hay chance de sesión corta?","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c971578aa88191b34e060790cf660d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":12248,"output":148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12396,"cost":{"input":0.03062,"output":0.00222,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03284}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774809426621,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9715559048191bc07c7c021f78313"}}
