{"type":"message","id":"8a5d3b5d","parentId":"0887ea23","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:24:36.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Sí: **martes toca pierna**.\n\nQueda así:\n- lunes no se arma como base\n- martes se retoma\n- y se retoma con **pernitas**, no improvisando otra cosa\n\nYa con eso hay dirección clara.\nEl martes es para volver a ejecutar, no para volver a discutir qué toca.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9ecf5a2e88191954dac38d0f00366\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":354,"output":76,"cacheRead":14848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15278,"cost":{"input":0.000885,"output":0.00114,"cacheRead":0.003712,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005737}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774841070506,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9ecf3716c8191ac5eb9bbd1af57f3"}}
