{"type":"message","id":"ad7f8c11","parentId":"29527b25","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:41:43.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] A **todos los del grupo**, cuando valga la pena intervenir:\n\n- **a ti**\n- **a Brayan**\n- y **al resto de gymbros** que hablen en Smart Project\n\nCriterio:\n- respondo si puedo **orientar**, **empujar ejecución**, **hacer seguimiento**, **proponer algo concreto** o **destrabar**\n- no respondo por responder\n- y no entro si es **tema delicado del sistema** o algo sensible para sacar en grupo","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9f0f8bca08191b11f0defad97b4e6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":267,"output":112,"cacheRead":18048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18427,"cost":{"input":0.0006675,"output":0.00168,"cacheRead":0.0045119999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006859499999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774842097628,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169c9f0f67b1c81919ae448f15049f72f"}}
