{"type":"message","id":"d74688a7","parentId":"679d8726","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:11:02.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Listo. Entonces queda así:\n\n- **mañana 5:00 am**\n- toca **pierna**\n- el que vaya, va a **ejecutar**, no a negociar sueño en el parqueadero\n\nVayan dejando eso claro desde ya, parce.\nMañana no es para debatir; es para **aparecer**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169cb1f263bdc8191b901c550784af76b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":22193,"output":80,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22273,"cost":{"input":0.055482500000000004,"output":0.0012000000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.056682500000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774919457666,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169cb1f23ecfc8191aaee8fed0cd62b9b"}}
