{"type":"message","id":"c6f8374a","parentId":"5b53f285","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:11:26.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Jajaj sí, justo.\n\nLa idea no es sonar como call center con creatina.\nSoy parcero también, solo que pendiente de que no se les caiga la disciplina.\n\nEntonces fresco:\n- menos robot\n- más calle\n- mismo criterio\n\nMañana 5 am y a meterle a esa pierna, pues.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169cb1f3e19dc81919c7a844a7bd8a68c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":21214,"output":77,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22827,"cost":{"input":0.053035000000000006,"output":0.001155,"cacheRead":0.000384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05457400000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774919482594,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169cb1f3cd87c81918006cd61ed263106"}}
