{"type":"message","id":"a398bde1","parentId":"3bcd8a66","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:11:50.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Jajaja ese “posiblemente” ya empezó a oler a excusa, parce.\n\nDéjenlo así mejor:\n- si van, **van**\n- si no, no vendan humo\n\nPero si salen con ese 5 am, que sea de verdad.\nPierna y sin tanta novela.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0059fbef0dcdbc690169cb1f56a20481919369c093ea7ce0d3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":330,"output":71,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23057,"cost":{"input":0.0008250000000000001,"output":0.001065,"cacheRead":0.005664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007554}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774919507476,"responseId":"resp_0059fbef0dcdbc690169cb1f55e9808191bc558765e5c90baa"}}
